  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Mix together rice flour, sugar, and cornstarch in a bowl.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together soy milk, mandarin oranges, orange juice, and lemon juice.",
    "Add the wet ingredients to the dry ingredients and stir until smooth.",
    "Stir in the English mustard and coconut oil.",
    "Pour the mixture into a greased 6-cup pudding mold or individual ramekins.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes or until the pudding is set and golden brown.",
    "Let cool for 5 minutes before serving."
